  ('dietitian-moex-00443', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於細胞骨架（cytoskeleton）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["作用於維持和改變細胞形狀、產生細胞位移以及參與細胞分裂", "肌動蛋白絲（actin filaments）之間能互相快速組合（assembly）", "已組成的中間絲（intermediate filaments）結構穩定且較不易解離（disassembled）", "微管（microtubules）由多種類型蛋白組成，直徑比中間絲（intermediate filaments）小"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4b45a176e23e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "84b9ea3552b5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
