  ('dietitian-moex-00445', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為骨骼肌發生低血鈣強直（hypocalcemic tetany）的主要原因？', '["細胞內之鈣離子無法經由主動運輸而被回收至肌漿網（sarcoplasmic reticulum）", "細胞外之低鈣濃度環境會造成細胞膜發生去極化現象，以及產生自發性動作電位", "細胞質中之肌球蛋白輕鏈激酶（myosin light chain kinase）持續磷酸化橫橋（cross-bridge）", "細胞質中之鈣離子與攜鈣素（calmodulin）複合體持續結合於肌動蛋白（actin）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4b45a176e23e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "84b9ea3552b5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
